message.content:
1. Can you provide evidence to support the claim that the Indian cricket team came last in the super six stage in the 1999 Cricket World Cup?
2. Is there credible information available to confirm that India has been knocked out 4 times in the group stage of the ICC Cricket World Cup in the years 1975, 1979, 1992, and 2007?
3. Are there reliable sources to confirm the specific details of India's performance in the ICC Cricket World Cup across the years mentioned in the statement?
